  "title": "💼 Brand Promotions & Sales Support Associate ✨",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>Start Building Your Career with Hands-On Experience</strong> 🌟</p><p>Are you looking to gain real-world exposure in branding, promotions, and sales? We’re looking for motivated individuals to join our team and learn through practical experience in marketing campaigns, events, and customer engagement.</p><p>This role is ideal for candidates who are eager to learn, grow, and develop professional skills in a supportive team environment.</p><h3>What You’ll Do:</h3><p>🎯 Support brand promotions, events, and on-site campaigns<br />🎯 Engage customers and communicate brand messages clearly<br />🎯 Assist with sales support and customer acquisition activities<br />🎯 Work closely with team leaders to meet campaign objectives<br />🎯 Learn essential skills in communication, teamwork, and sales execution</p><h3>What We’re Looking For:</h3><p>✅ ITE graduates or individuals starting their career<br />✅ Positive attitude and willingness to learn<br />✅ Comfortable interacting with people face-to-face<br />✅ Able to work in team-based, on-site environments (events & roadshows)<br />✅ No prior experience required — full training provided</p><h3>Why Join Us?</h3><p>🌱 Structured training and on-the-job guidance<br />🌱 Clear development and progression opportunities<br />🌱 Exposure to branding, promotions, and sales operations<br />🌱 Supportive, energetic, and collaborative team culture<br />🌱 Opportunity to build confidence and leadership skills over time</p><p><strong>This role is suitable for candidates seeking entry-level experience and skills development.</strong></p>",
